---
title: Chorizo Crusted Baked Rigatoni with Cheese and Garlicky Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: This Chorizo Crusted Baked Rigatoni is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-crusted-baked-rigatoni-55c948f4.jpg
